PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Public Works and Government Services of LOUIS PROULX, of Laval, Quebec, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Royal Canadian Mint to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Diane Marleau, whose term has expired.
